api_list.name: Text_to_speech_v1_text_to_speech__voice_id__post
api_list.description: Converts text into speech using a voice of your choice and returns audio.

required_parameters.name: voice_id
required_parameters.description: Voice ID to be used, you can use https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/voices to list all the available voices.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://my-elevenlabs-io.p.rapidapi.com/v1/text-to-speech/21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "my-elevenlabs-io.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: Edit_voice_v1_voices__voice_id__edit_post
api_list.description: Edit a voice created by you.

required_parameters.name: name
required_parameters.description: The name that identifies this voice. This will be displayed in the dropdown of the website.

required_parameters.name: voice_id
required_parameters.description: Voice ID to be used, you can use https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/voices to list all the available voices.

optional_parameters.name: files
optional_parameters.description: Audio files to add to the voice

optional_parameters.name: labels
optional_parameters.description: Serialized labels dictionary for the voice.

api_list.name: Add_voice_v1_voices_add_post
api_list.description: Add a new voice to your collection of voices in VoiceLab.

required_parameters.name: name
required_parameters.description: The name that identifies this voice. This will be displayed in the dropdown of the website.

required_parameters.name: files
required_parameters.description: One or more audio files to clone the voice from

optional_parameters.name: labels
optional_parameters.description: Serialized labels dictionary for the voice.
